      "text": {
        "intro": [
          "Word arrives from the sect: the time has come to return to Azure Peaks. The invitation is not made lightly.",
          "The mountain road is long, and the qi grows denser with every league — the air itself pushing back against those not ready."
        ],
        "body": [
          "For a sect disciple, the journey back to the heights is both privilege and trial. The path recognises only those who have earned their place."
        ]
